column5: hey there, I was wondering if anyone could help me trailer a boat to the Marina in Markham for $50.  The boat is also in Markham.  I will also accept borrowing a suitable vehicle for one hour.  8km distance.
sent a pm Sat saying could have done it Sunday, but received no response.   gl
For 50$ I would be willing to bet you could rent a Uhaul pickup truck and tow it. Look into it. Its 20$+ mileage. Doesn't sound like you need to go far.
If it's only 8k, have you talked to the marina about them coming and getting it themselves ??
